data.description: One & a half block from bay access! Charming 2 story home boasts 4 large bedrooms (2 downstairs) and 2 updated bathrooms. You are greeted by a light-filled family room. Attached to the family room is a flex space that can be open or closed off by French doors. The dining room is open to the kitchen which includes all appliances. The utility room has plenty of space for the washer, dryer, storage, & a sink. Upstairs, you will find 2 huge bedrooms with a walk-in closet of your dreams! Outside, the fenced in yard offers privacy. There is ample storage in the garage & the 2 storage sheds, one of which has a deck & outdoor sink area. Fresh paint! Buyer to receive credit at closing when using Seller's trusted lending partner Kendall Ormsby with RW Towne Mortgage.
